title: Why cannot I import the tpprof module?
body_html: From this line I get to know that the new added profile tool is imported, but it seems strange: 1) it cannot be imported from the interactive interface; 2) and when mnist is run it raise the same error saying ImportError: cannot import name 'tfprof_log_pb2'. What happened for the newly added feature?

body: From [this line](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/tfprof/python/tools/tfprof/tfprof_logger.py#L30) I get to know that the new added profile tool is imported, but it seems strange: 1) it cannot be imported from the interactive interface; 2) and when mnist is run it raise the same error saying `ImportError: cannot import name 'tfprof_log_pb2'`. What happened for the newly added feature?
